    "writeback_targets remains the current Stage9 legacy runtime carrier; authoritative_base_targets is the canonical owner field for source-ownership adjudication.",
    "Outcome taxonomy owns only the base target set; governance, payment_exception, delivery_exception, and upstream feedback loop targets are additive or projected-only per writeback contract.",
    "DELIVERY_ABANDONED may keep governance_feedback_event only as a catalog-declared legacy runtime compatibility target; the canonical owner of governance_feedback_event remains governance_taxonomy.",
